</mei>

<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- m1-4: "33" root position triads, light opening. F-A in RH, F-C-F in LH.
  Occasional "43" 1st inversion at V chords for stepwise bass motion.
- m5-8: Quartal color "44" at I chords (F-Bb), standard triads at V.
  Provides modern, open sound for the repetition section.
- m9-12: Development section uses "333" 7th chord voicings (A2-E3-A3-C4 for Am7,
  Bb2-F3-Bb3-D4 for BbΔ). Richer texture as hymn reaches c5 in melody.
